  "keyFeatures": [
    "26 focused SKILL.md files covering the full Compose performance loop: Measure, Diagnose, Fix, Verify",
    "Symptom-to-skill index for rapid lookup by error symptom or API name",
    "Install script for Claude Code, Android Studio Agent, and Gemini with flat-layout symlinks",
    "Stability skills: compiler report parsing, stability config, CI enforcement, IDE plugin integration",
    "Recomposition skills: state deferral, derivedStateOf, strong skipping, subcomposition pitfalls",
    "Lazy layout skills: stable keys, contentType, LazyLayoutCacheWindow, pausable prefetch",
