    "Side effect skills: collectAsStateWithLifecycle, LaunchedEffect vs RememberedEffect",
    "Measurement skills: Macrobenchmark, Baseline Profiles, release mode invariants",
    "Hot Reload skills: Compose HotSwan setup, AI-agent MCP loop, state preservation"
